     C* E19: look-ahead field reads the next record's value.
     C* When CUR=20, the look-ahead NEXT should be 30.
     FLADATA  IP  F    80              DISK
     FLAOUT   O   F    132             PRINTER
     ILADATA      AA
     I                                     1   2   0CUR
     I        AA  **
     I                                     1   2   0NEXT
     C           CUR       COMP 20                       10
     C  10                 Z-ADDNEXT      RPGRET
